{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 7331488}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por resoluci&#xF3;n exenta N&#xBA;2.128 de 26 de julio de 2006 de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, autor&#xED;zase a PESQUERA ITATA S.A., para realizar actividades extractivas en aguas internacionales con la nave &quot;Allipen I&quot;, cuyas caracter&#xED;sticas n&#xE1;uticas son las siguientes:</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Se&#xF1;al distintiva&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CB-4493</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Puerto de Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Valpara&#xED;so</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2685</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Eslora de arqueo&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 47,30&nbsp; &nbsp;  m</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  T.R.G. (Internacional)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  786,00</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Manga&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  10,40&nbsp; &nbsp;  m</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Puntal&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  6,00&nbsp; &nbsp;  m.</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  D&#xE9;jase sin efecto la resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA;2.323 de 2005, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a de Pesca, en virtud del contenido de la presente resoluci&#xF3;n.</div><br></div>", "i": 7331489}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Valpara&#xED;so, 26 de julio de 2006.- Carlos Hern&#xE1;ndez Salas, Subsecretario de Pesca.</div><br></div>", "i": 7331490}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctrina": [], "metadatos": {"tiene_notas": false, "tipos_numeros": [{"tipo": "3", "numero": "2128 EXENTA", "abreviacion": "RES", "descripcion": "Resolucion", "compuesto": "RES-2128 EXENTA"}], "organismos": ["MINISTERIO DE ECONOMÍA", "FOMENTO Y RECONSTRUCCION", "SUBSECRETARIA